        Repairs vs Capital Improvements: The Tax Difference Brisbane Property Investors Must Understand
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Calling maintenance work a repair when the ATO considers it a capital improvement can create problems at tax time and at sale. Here is how to tell the difference.
      </p>
    </div>
